Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Không vấn đề gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Đừng lại đây. Deku.
